[SPEAKER_00] And it is interesting to note that the true authorship of the work,

162
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] was reprinted at least four times more until 1898.

163
00:23:06,940 --> 00:23:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] The true authorship was disclosed only in 1888.

164
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] So, for more than one century, this book was reprinted again and again,

165
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] and it was not known who was the real author.

166
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] And finally, let me refer to the Croatian scholar Sanja Vulic,

167
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] who writes that, I quote,

168
00:23:29,940 --> 00:23:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] "Zarcelo Istine is remarkable not only for its numerous reprints.

169
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] What is more," she writes,

170
00:23:37,940 --> 00:23:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] "is that Pejkic was the one to open the doors for scores of works of a similar genre in Croatian literature.

171
00:23:46,940 --> 00:23:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Indeed, the controversy with orthodoxy represents the bulk of Croatian literary theological production,

172
00:23:53,940 --> 00:23:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] particularly in the 18th century."

173
00:23:56,940 --> 00:23:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] End of quote.

174
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] So, in sum, Pejkic's polemical works are a testimony coming from a period of deep division and hostility

175
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] between the Eastern and Western churches,

176
00:24:12,940 --> 00:24:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] during which the discourse on doctrinal issues had the character of a religious and political propaganda.

177
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] Yet, they may be enlightening for us today,

178
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] because they offer a, so to say, horizontal view of the division of the churches,

179
00:24:29,940 --> 00:24:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] not the view of an erudite theologian,

180
00:24:33,940 --> 00:24:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] but of a missionary in the field,

181
00:24:36,940 --> 00:24:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] whose attitude towards both the practice of faith and the dialogue, so to say,

182
00:24:41,940 --> 00:24:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] with the orthodox hierarchy and people was a very pragmatic one.

183
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] And thank you for your attention.

184
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:54,259
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

